      #[i.fa.fa-bars(aria-hidden="true")]
    .off-canvas__content.off-canvas__content--left.off-canvas__content--lg.bg--gray-lighten-2#oc-ex-2(style="width:200px")
      .off-canvas__close.off-canvas__close--right.
        #[i.fa.fa-times(aria-hidden="true")]
      | Example 2: off-canvas sidebar content
    | Demo 2: this off-canvas sidebar has #[code style="width:200px"].

    br
